{"id":14254,"date":"2013-05-18T12:08:49","date_gmt":"2013-05-18T08:08:49","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=14254"},"modified":"2019-05-31T18:44:44","modified_gmt":"2019-05-31T14:44:44","slug":"images-fabric-patterns","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/18\/images-fabric-patterns\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Images: Fabric with patterns, inscriptions on it"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&#8216;Ubaydullah ibn Abdullah reported: He entered the home of Abu Talhah when he was sick and he found Sahl ibn Hunayf with him. Abu Talhah called for someone to remove a sheet that was underneath him. Sahl said to him, &#8220;Why did you remove it?&#8221; Abu Talhah said, &#8220;Because there were images on it and you know what the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said about it.&#8221; Sahl said, &#8220;Did not the Prophet also say: <strong>Except for patterns on fabric?<\/strong>&#8221; Abu Talhah said, &#8220;Of course, but this makes me feel better.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1750<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Sahih<\/i><\/b> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u062a\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u062f\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u064a\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0633\u064e\u0647\u